description: Growing not far from the coast.

Locality: Bako NP, Sarawak
Habitat: MDF to KF
Local Name: Gaharu buaya
Description: Tree 25m, 40cm dbh. Light to dark green leaves. Fibrous leaves, similar to those of Aquilaria spp. Smooth crackling stem, dark greyish colour. Inner bark is yellowish, with a thick and leathery texture. Dark colour resin produces a light aromatic scent.
